<item>
            <title>[PPLNS-7817] Migrate to Call Miner Bulk Export API</title>
                <link>https://theverygroup.atlassian.net/browse/PPLNS-7817</link>
                <project id="20015" key="PPLNS">Data Enablement</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Implement the transition from the current Callminer export process to the new Bulk Export API to support Speech Analytics data ingestion.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The goal is to migrate to the new API without disrupting the existing Speech Analytics pipeline. Support from the Data team will be required to ensure the transition is seamless and downstream consumers experience no interruption.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This work will introduce a new ingestion mechanism for Callminer exports and ensure that exported files are securely retrieved, processed, and loaded into the lakehouse.&lt;/p&gt;



